Class ID

java.lang.Object
  edu.cmu.lti.oaqa.bio.resource_wrapper.ID

public class ID
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a system ID from some authority. Contains two strings: name of the authority, identifier given by that authority. Ex HGNC:1100 (BRCA1) Ex Vega:OTTHUMG00000157426 (BRCA1)
